commitResults.messageBody:
ExchangeRateManager class consist of the following main features:
- Loading exchange rates from a text file specified in the class
- Saving the exchange rate whenever user updates it
- Convert currency
- show supported currecencies
- show exchange rates

Add currency conversion function to ExpenseParser class to convert currency if applicable.

Debugs:
- Change Commands abstract class to Command
ExchangeRateFileHandler is for loading/saving exchange rates from /data/ExchangeRates.txt to the ExchangeRateManager
